metadata.name: GOATNET GENESIS CRDNTL
metadata.description:
- GOATNET Genesis CRDNTL offers lifetime membership to GOATNET. GOATNET is a content platform empowering its community to own and participate in the greatest attractions of the creator economy.
- **Member benefits include:**
- 	• Lifetime access to content and one premiere event
- 	• Visibility into unlimited Proposed Attractions
- 	• Receive a "Chip"/swag in the making of Goatnet
